data.description: This amazing home is a must-see with all that it has to offer! With the charming front yard landscaping and covered front porch, it allows for the perfect place to relax and enjoy the view. Upon entering the home you are greeted with a large entryway with views of the stunning vaulted wood beamed ceilings, and wood stove on a raised hearth, in the living room providing warmth and character. The kitchen has been beautifully updated with maple cabinets, granite countertops, double ovens-with the lower one also working as a convection oven, three lazy susans in the cabinets for convenient storage, and a raised mixing stand hidden away in one of the cabinets. So much privacy to offer with the split floor plan. The primary suite is on one side of the home and the additional two bedrooms are on the other side with a bathroom to share. Your primary suite boasts a large walk-in closet, double sinks, updated flooring in the bedroom, and a door leading to the tranquil backyard. Sit back and relax on your back deck while enjoying the beauty of the trees and fresh air.
